<title>Desktop features affected by firewall</title>

  <p>Some features of the GNOME desktop require local networking and certain
  ports to be open; firewalls can interfere with this. The following features
  particularly tend to have problems with firewall:</p>
  
<list>
	<item><p>printer discovery</p></item>
	<item><p>personal file sharing</p></item>
	<item><p>media sharing</p></item>
</list>


